identity.description:
Automatically discovers and loads tools from the Human Expert Feedback MCP Server for consulting on complex medical decisions.

Automatically discover and load all tools from Human Expert Feedback MCP Server. Provides tools for consulting human experts on complex medical decisions.
capabilities: Automatically discover and load tools from the Human Expert Feedback MCP Server
Enable consultation with human experts on complex medical decisions

purpose.model:
SentenceTransformer(

  (2): Normalize()
)
